Package medit.ActionManagers

This package contains ActionManagers for main form

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AboutActionManager
    This action manager was splitted a little bit uselessly, but to keep structure of MEdit, it's there.
    BottombarActionManager
    This class is small, but it was needed to split it away from MainFrame to keep code climate and internal structure of MEdit.
    CodeCompletionActionManager
    This very important class is setting up code completion for MEdit
    EditActionManager
    This big class is a bit different from other ActionManagers, because it's split into many methods.
    FileActionManager
    This class is big and unusual among other ActionManagers, like EditActionManager.
    LanguageActionManager
    This is propably best organized actionmanager in the whole project.
    PrintActionManager
    This class is adding print support for MEdit.
    ScriptsActionManager
    This class is allowing user to script MEdit using own scripts written in B++.
    TextOPActionManager
    This class contains code, that is embedding items into Text Operations menu.
    ThemesActionManager
    This class is creating menu items for each of themes available in MEdit.
    TimerTaskActionManager
    This very important class is setting up timers, which free memory every 60seconds, if amount of used memory is bigger or equal to 200mb.
    ToolActionManager
    This class is nearly copy+paste of ScriptActionManager.
    WindowActionManager
    This function is watching on amount of MainFrame instances and exiting program, if there are no instances left.
